A real-time facial emotion detection system built with Python, OpenCV, and DeepFace. The system captures live webcam footage, detects faces, classifies emotions (e.g., happy, sad, angry, fear, surprise, neutral), logs emotional trends over time, and plots emotion statistics â€” all in real-time!

